title: Heist Editor v3.5.16.1 - GTA V Online v1.68
text:
Up-to-date and working cheat Heist Editor V3.5.16.1 for the next update of the game GTA V Online. This is a small tool with which you can manage all the robberies in the GTA 5 game.

For example, you can edit the apartment robbery, the doomsday robbery, the casino robbery and the percentage of the player of the cayo-perico robbery. Additionally, you can edit the potential capture of the casino and the real result of the mission, or you can edit the real capture of Cayo Perico. Other additional functionality is also available, for example, you can add armor, repair a car or sell it.

A:You need unlock all access points and POI before start the last mission.
